1
00:00:00,720 --> 00:00:08,720
In the Age of Ancients, the world
was unformed, shrouded by fog.

2
00:00:11,220 --> 00:00:17,800
A land of grey crags, arch-trees,
and everlasting dragons.

3
00:00:23,940 --> 00:00:31,940
But then there was fire,
and to his fire came disparity.

4
00:00:35,760 --> 00:00:44,760
Heat and cold, life and death,
and of course, light and dark.

5
00:00:53,240 --> 00:01:02,240
Then, from the dark, they came, and
found the souls of lords within the flame.

6
00:01:11,720 --> 00:01:15,340
Nito, the first of the dead.

7
00:01:22,580 --> 00:01:28,580
The witch of Izalith, and
her daughters of Chaos.

8
00:01:29,340 --> 00:01:34,700
Gwyn, the lord of sunlight,
and his faithful knights.

9
00:01:38,101 --> 00:01:45,920
And the furtive pygmy, so easily forgotten.

10
00:01:49,900 --> 00:01:56,400
With the strength of lords,
they challenged the dragons.

11
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:04,400
Gwyn's mighty gods
peeled apart their stone-skills.

12
00:02:06,301 --> 00:02:09,480
The witches weaved great fire-stores.

13
00:02:13,781 --> 00:02:17,360
Nito unleashed a piasma
of death and disease.

14
00:02:21,961 --> 00:02:27,060
And Seath, the scaleless betrayed his
own, and the dragons were no more.

15
00:02:42,060 --> 00:02:47,060
Thus began the Age of Fire.

16
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:59,360
But soon the flames will
fade, and only dark will remain.

17
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:14,260
Even now there are only embers, and man
sees not light, but only endless lights.

18
00:03:18,060 --> 00:03:26,060
And amongst the living are seen,
carriers of the accursed darksign.

